{
  "stem": "7506.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we-- I walked with the men, my father, and we say Kaddish for him.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Walking along the barbed wire until the end of the barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then the cart thing, the wagon carried on to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "This happened in 1944, in the same year that we arrived in the camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1944 I was 12.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My mother tells me that he always suffered with some disability, but I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I don't know what he died of in the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So what with that and my father being in the bunker, towards the end of 1944, probably around about November or October, winter starts.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's very cold.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's very hot there in the summer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The whole camp was surrounded by pine trees.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You couldn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was just wherever you looked was pine trees or other parts of the camp were the watchtowers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the main road through the camp, which was not a normal main road.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the camp's main road.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On the 4th of December in 1944, I think that was the biggest change in my life in the camp, And.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Indeed, I think the biggest change, the biggest happening in my life, which has affected my life, my whole life, to this day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "As you know, or you may know, in Holland, we celebrate a holiday called Saint Nicholas, which is celebrated the 5th of December every year.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It is something which is residual to the time when Holland was under Spanish occupation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So children all celebrate Saint Nicholas, in a way even more than Christmas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It is a time of presents and a nice story.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
